#: 603579bbb6b34b96b6a630ed2ca79da3 of
#: tensormesh.element.element.Element.eval_cell_jacobian:16
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
":math:`\\frac{\\partial \\phi_b}{\\partial x_i}` is the derivative of "
