msgid ""
"Simplex ordering: vertex nodes first, then edge nodes, then interior "
"nodes. The facets are line segments. Type strings: ``\"triangle\"`` "
"(linear), ``\"triangle6\"``, ``\"triangle10\"``, …, ``\"triangle66\"``."
msgstr ""

