msgid ""
"Tensor-product Lagrange nodes in **lexicographic** order — note this "
"differs from the Gmsh/VTK boundary-spiral order, so loading external "
"high-order quads must go through :meth:`Element.reorder`. The facets are "
"line segments. Type strings: ``\"quad\"`` (linear), ``\"quad8\"``, "
"``\"quad9\"``, ``\"quad16\"``, …, ``\"quad121\"``."
msgstr ""

#: 936a55beeeb543a88e3c3b6cf3ed3f73 of tensormesh.element.element.Tetrahedron:1
msgid ""
