"(1,0,0), (0,1,0), (0,0,1)`."
msgstr ""

#: 64dcf3670bdf41249650a81e62c3cf48 of tensormesh.element.element.Tetrahedron:4
msgid ""
"Simplex ordering: vertex / edge / face / interior groupings, with indices"
" within each group following the TensorMesh convention (see :ref:`node-"
"ordering-gallery`). The facets are triangles. Type strings: ``\"tetra\"``"
" (linear), ``\"tetra10\"``, ``\"tetra20\"``, …, ``\"tetra286\"``."
msgstr ""

