msgstr ""

#: 62e02a950a0f406dac9c286ff98bd820 of tensormesh.element.element.Hexahedron:3
msgid ""
"Tensor-product Lagrange nodes in **lexicographic** order — note this "
"differs substantially from Gmsh/VTK, which walks along edges. The facets "
"are quadrilaterals. Type strings: ``\"hexahedron\"`` (linear), "
"``\"hexahedron20\"``, ``\"hexahedron27\"``, ``\"hexahedron64\"``, …, "
"``\"hexahedron1000\"``."
msgstr ""

#: a9a13c8a0e4944449bdc6b3237595dca of tensormesh.element.element.Prism:1
